snippet.title: 「Constant Moderato」 Piano Performance (2023 Ver.) / Blue archive Login Screen OST "Theme 1"
snippet.description:
Blue Archive - Login Screen OST 「Constant Moderato」 Piano Performance (2023 Ver.)


* This work is a remastered version of the sound source, the video may not match.


Today's performance is Blue Archive's Legend song "Constant Moderato".

Almost simultaneously with the opening of Korean and global servers
This is an early performance song that was uploaded to my channel.

Today, Blue Archive was officially opened in China.
To celebrate this, I remastered the performance and sound.

And there's a real reason why I reworked this original song.
What is it? Hahahahaha The truth will come later~~

Thank you for listening.

---------------------------------------------------
Discord Channel : https://discord.gg/TGvwJR9rs7
Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano
---------------------------------------------------
「Gregorius」 Piano Epic Performance (Full Ver.) : https://youtu.be/2Gn1mqF0OEc
4th PV 「RE Aoharu」 Piano & KR Ver. (Subtitled) : https://youtu.be/WWYLDYWWhHI
Blue Archive Memorial BGM 「Midnight Trip」 Piano Play : https://youtu.be/VLaDJCDIA8Q
Blue Archive 1st Anniversary PV OST(Luminous Memory) Piano Play : https://youtu.be/1xhW91bbFS8
---------------------------------------------------
템플릿 : 론박자막연구소
---------------------------------------------------
